    "title": "Portfolio Manager",
    "excerpt": "<p>The Office of Data and Innovation (ODI) is seeking an experienced Portfolio Manager (ITM II). This role involves comprehensive management of department-wide projects and portfolios, including providing strategic direction, ensuring timely completion, and managing resources effectively. A core responsibility will be serving as the dedicated project manager for multiple external, high-profile programs, operating under the &#8230; <a title=\"Portfolio Manager\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/join-us/portfolio-manager/\" aria-label=\"More on Portfolio Manager\">Read more</a></p>\n",
